name: Where is it?
description:
Where is it?

This is the second rotoscoped collage in the "Fragments" collectible series. A small fragment of time, a moment, a memory, a question.
Each piece was created with Photoshop and After Effects, the videos were rotoscoped to obtain the animation and immerse it in a new universe.

////

¿Dónde está?

Este es el segundo collage rotoscópico de la serie coleccionable "Fragmentos". Un pequeño fragmento de tiempo, un momento, un recuerdo, una pregunta.
Cada pieza fue creada con Photoshop y After Effects, los videos fueron rotoscopiados para obtener la animación y sumergirla en un nuevo universo.
